{"tid":1457742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日柒到仆街 原因只有一個","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:35:32.000Z","uid":90610,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"436661dfe39f0bd9ced07915288bb737efa5c50f","tid":1457742,"uid":90610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"主要原因唔係因為有鬼<br />\n而係大家已經覺得香港既黑警已經唔會講道理<br />\n無講 示威者做咩都好 都會施以暴力<br />\n<br />\n記者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 俾人爆頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n飲湯行過既市民 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俾人打後腦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個手無寸鐵既女仔<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俾人爆眼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係啲狗未習慣性放催淚彈之前 <br />\n我地以為 商場 地鐵係安全既<br />\n邊有人會諗過 佢地會衝去商場捉人<br />\n邊有人會諗過 啲狗 會好似白衣人咁衝閘打人 用鎗射人<br />\n<br />\n淨睇今日既結果 係 無錯 散水撚7左<br />\n但係<br />\n我想講 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港無一個地方係絕對既安全</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"aa5011c5c510ea4e6294ea6405bc04f7157e9ff4","tid":1457742,"uid":90610,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"唔好怪大家 散左<br />\n咪番去lor<br />\n<br />\n唔係好大件事"},{"pid":"19699f82d88875d76f9a1fe1c0e1c505f3718d98","tid":1457742,"uid":90610,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"最緊要 大家仲係到<br />\n大家既目標仲係一致"},{"pid":"b457454c6a234a133416b4c87b7b1f0cf09dc252","tid":1457742,"uid":32226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"真 路好長 共免之"},{"pid":"904d3f8c581051137fe42ac542a8889b795f4a01","tid":1457742,"uid":90610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b457454c6a234a133416b4c87b7b1f0cf09dc252","tid":1457742,"uid":32226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"真 路好長 共免之"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"無錯 <br />\n一次既錯失 只要大家仲係到<br />\n我地就有機會成功"}